n.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A8n/H%C3%AD-%C4%91%E1%BB%81-Xu-Ng%C3%B4n-th%E1%BA%A3o-c%C3%A1c-tam-th%E1%BA%ADp-nh%E1%BB%8B-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-1xg3hi80FKcKoSCSEece2g">Hí đề Xu Ngôn thảo các tam thập nhị vận - 戲題樞言草閣三十二韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A8n/author-9iJ5oLtFQBkuT0Ej5xvn9Q">Lý Thương Ẩn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/Ng%C3%B4n-ho%C3%A0i/poem-2RznRK5MAxVa5OynEKShTA">Ngôn hoài - 言懷</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/author-14GcnhLjD2ajP0MTgtX13Q">Ngô Thì Nhậm</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90o%C3%A0n-Huy%C3%AAn/Ti%E1%BB%85n-b%E1%BA%A3n-b%E1%BB%99-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-th%C6%B0-Phan-V%E1%BB%8B-Ch%E1%BB%89-%C4%91%E1%BA%A1i-nh%C3%A2n-h%C6%B0u-tr%C3%AD/poem-Eh4UstTjyO_3CZ7hWLLAyQ">Tiễn bản bộ thượng thư Phan Vị Chỉ đại nhân hưu trí - 餞本部尚書潘渭沚大人休致</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90o%C3%A0n-Huy%C3%AAn/author-h3EvqeQvlQUxq2sceUWWYQ">Đoàn Huyên</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-%C3%8Dch-T%E1%BA%AFc/Xu%E1%BA%A5t-qu%E1%BB%91c/poem-UK-2GvtOe_wbSd4b-DuJ7w">Xuất quốc - 出國</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-%C3%8Dch-T%E1%BA%AFc/author-2WHplYhGibS3kNKVcV5ntg">Trần Ích Tắc</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
